file.name: issue_1433-resolve-schema-without-type.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  title: no type resolution
  version: 1.0.0
paths:
  /foo:
    post:
      requestBody:
        required: true
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/FooInput'
      responses:
        '200':
          description: subscription successfully created
components:
  schemas:
    FooInput:
      properties:
        bar:
          type: string
        input:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/BazInput'
    BazInput:
      properties:
        baz:
          type: string
